<p><em>Note: The next test includes a perfectly functional RAM. I have been asked by ███ ███████, who forgot to save their latest protocol, to recover this document for them. Despite several attempts to explain that the recovery is almost impossible, they have insisted on this test. -Laskenta</em></p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong> One Foundation double data rate synchronous dynamic random-access memory (16GB)<br />
<strong>Setting:</strong> Fine<br />
