<p><em>Note: Permission to give this to ███ ███████, when the check-up is finished and no sensitive/anomalous data was found? -Laskenta</em></p>
<p><em>Note: Granted, if <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/new-technical-issues">Rosen</a> allows it. - Veritas</em></p>
