<p><em>Note: It's quite&#8230; small. Given the amount of metal that was in the input, I'm not that surprised by the size of the output. Although&#8230; have you seen the quality of the tamahagane? The rifle doesn't even need a paint job to look absolutely amazing. - J.R. Kai</em></p>
