<strong>Output:</strong> A completely black orb that is about 20 centimeters in diameter and is capable of flotation. Similarly to the previous output, the orb absorbs all wavelengths of light with 100% efficiency. Additionally, after absorbing enough light, a concentrated beam will be shot out from the orb, has been recorded penetrating up to 2.5 meter of reinforced concrete. Object placed in anomalous storage due to the risk on an accidental discharge if incineration was attempted.</p>
